## ğŸ¯ Key Features Breakdown

### 1. **Main Feed**
- 10+ recipe categories (Breakfast, Lunch, Dinner, Dessert, etc.)
- Horizontal scrolling category selection
- Real-time recipe filtering by category
- Recipe cards with favorites toggle

### 2. **Recipe Details**
- Complete recipe information display
- Ingredients list with checkmarks
- Step-by-step instructions
- Nutritional information (calories, prep time, servings)
- Difficulty level indicator
- Favorite toggle functionality

### 3. **Favorites System**
- Heart icon toggle on recipe cards
- Dedicated favorites screen
- Persistent favorites tracking
- Empty state handling

### 4. **My Food Section**
- Personal recipe management
- Add new recipes with comprehensive form
- Edit existing recipes
- Delete recipes with confirmation
- User recipe badge identification

### 5. **Recipe Creation/Editing**
- Recipe name input
- Image URL support (extendable to upload)
- Dynamic ingredients list (add/remove)
- Step-by-step instructions (add/remove)
- Nutritional information inputs
- Category selection
- Save/Cancel functionality

## ğŸ› ï¸ Technical Stack

- **React Native Expo** - Cross-platform development
- **React Navigation** - Stack and Tab navigation
- **React Native Vector Icons** - Icon library
- **React Hooks** - State management
